name: evolution
description: Look at evolution | Look around you, watch and think how trees came to be what they are, branching and trying to reach the sky, but never reach it  | Life forms new forms, so different in different times, but still life | Life leaves traces and so do clouds when they travel through time, coloring the sky | How humans came to being what they are | How and when they started to create, build and believe in gods, in science, in arts, in space, in themselves | Humans tried so hard to reach the sky, and suddenly managed | Humans were first reaching the sky with their places of workship but then with planes, with rockets | When will life be multi planetary | Are we there to see it like a tree that branches towards the sky | evolution
